title: Jorma Kaukonen - Magic Two (1985; 1995) [FLAC]
description:
Jorma Kaukonen: Magic Two

Recorded live during Jorma's solo tour in 1984


Tracklist:

3. I'll Be Alright Someday
4. Embryonic Journey
5. Broken Highway
6. Candy Man
7. Follow The Drinking Gourd
8. Rock Me Baby
9. Another Man Done Gone
10. Roads And Roads &
11. Good Sheperd
12. Police Dog Blues

14. Man's Fate 


Personnel:

Jorma Kaukonen - acoustic guitar, vocals


Magic Two is an expanded re-release of the 1985 live album, Magic, containing performances of acoustic songs recorded during Jorma's solo tour in 1984.
